{"tid":2262842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國又發生恐襲  一男子教聖內被斬首","createTime":"2020-10-29T11:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T16:57:37.000Z","uid":76216,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"cb4978bd66697447d721cb81d92dfca89d5ec432","tid":2262842,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:43:28.000Z","msg":"快訊/法國尼斯恐攻釀2死！　1男慘遭「斬首」陳屍教堂內<br />\n<br />\nETtoday國際新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 記者吳美依／綜合外電報導<br />\n<br />\n綜合法媒《尼斯─馬汀報》（Nice-Matin）與俄羅斯《衛星通訊社》報導，法國尼斯一間<br />\n聖母院教堂於當地時間29日上午9時左右爆出槍響。兇嫌持刀攻擊人群，立刻引發恐慌，<br />\n目前累計2人死亡，多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尼斯市長埃斯特羅西（Christian Estrosi）在推特上指出，肇事者已被警察迅速逮捕。<br />\n另據消息指出，其中一名死者是年約70歲的男性，在教堂內遭到斬首死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201029/1842549.htm#ixzz6cFYG79Kl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201029%2F1842549.htm%23ixzz6cFYG79Kl&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KioL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=9251c49d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201029/1842549.htm#ixzz6cFYG79Kl</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇黎法國就黎宣戰<br />\n<br />\n十字軍 重現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685348b653f8d56e79e233a1afdb80c7b5e18b09","tid":2262842,"uid":243677,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:44:36.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新疆又唔見你班友去幫拖"},{"pid":"dfcf273d863a8d1c0df53880f9ea466f514faa66","tid":2262842,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:44:44.000Z","msg":"中國派出恐佈分子襲法國"},{"pid":"1cc129428ad0f98a25f11f60d2111678240eaa56","tid":2262842,"uid":378793,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:44:50.000Z","msg":"好彩香港淨係得溫和穆斯林<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"